        "body": "My original concept would be to start with a single 1D but very large array. Anything else should easily follow from that. Since communication will tend to be the bottleneck, there is less of a need to make any GPU-specific design choices. As noted, this has been done elsewhere, and should not be hard to express as a dask graph! ",
